							<p class="mb-4">AI-driven browser tool for extracting and summarizing text while ignoring markup and noise. Designed for OSINT and journalism workflows.</p>
							<div class="flex gap-2">
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-accent bg-opacity-10 text-accent rounded dark:bg-accent dark:bg-opacity-20">AI/ML</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-accent bg-opacity-10 text-accent rounded dark:bg-accent dark:bg-opacity-20">Browser</span>
