							<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-16 h-16 bg-secondary bg-opacity-10 rounded-bl-full dark:bg-secondary dark:bg-opacity-20"></div>
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 border-b-2 border-secondary pb-2 inline-block">SpotEye</h3>
							<p class="mb-4">Surveillance optimization tool that tags and prioritizes video events using smart filtering and human-in-the-loop learning.</p>
							<div class="flex gap-2">
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-secondary bg-opacity-10 text-secondary rounded dark:bg-secondary dark:bg-opacity-20">Video</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-secondary bg-opacity-10 text-secondary rounded dark:bg-secondary dark:bg-opacity-20">ML</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						
						<div class="card border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow p-6 relative overflow-hidden dark:border-gray-700">
							<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-16 h-16 bg-primary bg-opacity-10 rounded-bl-full dark:bg-primary dark:bg-opacity-20"></div>
							<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 border-b-2 border-primary pb-2 inline-block">XHashPass</h3>
							<p class="mb-4">A battle-tested evolution of my first tool ‚Äî Password generator. Lightweight, secure, and built with modern cryptographic standards in mind.</p>
							<div class="flex gap-2">
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary rounded dark:bg-primary dark:bg-opacity-20">Security</span>
								<span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary rounded dark:bg-primary dark:bg-opacity-20">Utility</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="text-center">
